      "rationale": "MMS verification confirmed second-order spatial convergence (observed order 1.94) for the incompressible Navier-Stokes solver on structured and unstructured meshes. Verification was performed under smooth, well-conditioned flow fields. Convergence behavior under near-singular conditions (e.g., zero-crossings in rotating-frame velocity, extreme aspect-ratio cells) was not part of the MMS suite."
    },
